Text: RE Electricity Summit websitestaying at Hotel Durant arriving very late Sun night so I cant do a Sunday dinner How about Monday lunch Rob Original Message From Mosher Allen mailto PPAnetorg Sent Thursday October PM To Subject RE Electricity Summit website How about a Sunday night alumniorganizer dinner in Berkeley I never did get to eat at Chez Panisse if its still good Id love to go there As I think I mentioned earlier Im going to have to miss the Monday evening dinner to fly to San Diego Im on a Tuesday morning NARUC Electricty Panel speaking on RTOs Allen Mosher Director of Policy Analysis American Public Power Association M Street NW Washington DC Voice Fax PPAnetorg Original Message From Heather Cameron SMTP Sent Friday October PM To Subject Electricity Summit website Dear Colleagues The new draft website is at eventselectricitysummitconferencehtm Have a good weekend Talk to you on Monday Best wishes Heather This email and any files transmitted with it are confidential and intended solely for the use of the individual or entity to whom they are addressed If you have received this email in error please notify the system manager at PPAnetorg This footnote also confirms that this email message has been swept for the presence of computer viruses PGE National Energy Group and any other company referenced herein that uses the PGE name or logo are not the same company as Pacific Gas and Electric Company the regulated California utility Neither PGE National Energy Group nor these other referenced companies are regulated by the California Public Utilities Commission Customers of Pacific Gas and Electric Company do not have to buy products from these companies in order to continue to receive quality regulated services from the utility
